{"tid":29114,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"廣島九州8日7夜行程","createTime":"2016-12-08T11:01:46.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T00:11:37.000Z","uid":10425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"490d9930e69f79765824a9adc2d885f65e9afee6","tid":29114,"uid":10425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:01:46.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲睇下有冇咩大問題 同有冇野推介<br />\n1月去 第一次去日本 1個人<br />\n係夜行巴士個到唔知點買飛 上網搵過又冇咩人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋hostel 通常最夜可以幾點check in<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nday1 17:15福岡落機 22:35夜行巴<br />\nday2 6點到廣島 宮島+廣島市 宿廣島<br />\nday3 原爆館+市內 22:30夜行巴返福岡<br />\ngay4 由布院+別府 宿別府<br />\nday5 門司港+小倉 宿博多<br />\nday6 長崎 宿長崎<br />\nday7 上午軍艦島 下午熊本 宿熊本/博多<br />\nday8 市內/6點機返香港"},{"pid":"0d89476cd40c2cbf2e9df7c768d0dec4ce838f5b","tid":29114,"uid":10425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:11:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd3239ebb840a820b43cbfbb02c283aba33d7f73","tid":29114,"uid":31629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:22:39.000Z","msg":"廣島就咪去8日九洲算啦"},{"pid":"a2dac72a8b02d9a1d5bc1fd7d12a3ef924638fa4","tid":29114,"uid":10425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T15:46:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廣島就咪去8日九洲算啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但8日九州又好似太多時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"981a8e639f1b6988139b37d62551a3b58a643863","tid":29114,"uid":5632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T16:12:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>廣島就咪去8日九洲算啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但8日九州又好似太多時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n伍寶八日北九州真係唔多，我上個月去完。<br />\n其中一日鳩行博多轉返長崎，咁就fit !<br />\n<br />\n落機晚餐番酒店<br />\n鳩行博多<br />\n門司港，杵築，小倉<br />\n九重夢吊橋，由布院<br />\n黑川溫泉<br />\n鳩行博多<br />\n佐賀行塗瓷神社同祐德稻荷神社<br />\n太宰府番香港"},{"pid":"33ee769a2688c9007d73689ec3f28548669e260e","tid":29114,"uid":10425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T00:25:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>廣島就咪去8日九洲算啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但8日九州又好似太多時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n伍寶八日北九州真係唔多，我上個月去完。<br />\n其中一日鳩行博多轉返長崎，咁就fit !<br />\n<br />\n落機晚餐番酒店<br />\n鳩行博多<br />\n門司港，杵築，小倉<br />\n九重夢吊橋，由布院<br />\n黑川溫泉<br />\n鳩行博多<br />\n佐賀行塗瓷神社同祐德稻荷神社<br />\n太宰府番香港</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你講d景點我都有睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但冇咩興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲諗緊今次去hea遊定充實d好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a07ca5e2cb6f8d0489be32450bb538ca1182615d","tid":29114,"uid":10425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T06:32:44.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打知阿蘇咩情況"},{"pid":"890a9927995fe35f0d5adb7841830d7be259ebb8","tid":29114,"uid":47775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T06:38:04.000Z","msg":"唔好去廣島 轉去南九州"},{"pid":"76ca1b655e74e1b96a53aa78c6075eb067f70a3f","tid":29114,"uid":2702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T14:03:02.000Z","msg":"巴打, 我四月會去9日九州<br />\n有咩地方好去?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e3dfae064281316541e895eadd9655373b1e13d","tid":29114,"uid":10425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T09:43:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打, 我四月會去9日九州<br />\n有咩地方好去?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都仲未去唔敢推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過我幾期待長崎個part<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定你有咩特別興趣"},{"pid":"9f7cdcedeebbe21eaa2c854e96b0a171dd2fa4f4","tid":29114,"uid":58081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T17:12:52.000Z","msg":"黎近我都係九州廣島<br />\n不過鹿兒島做起點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da8567d8dd5ea4b5c3a769210d0b7fc01007d7cb","tid":29114,"uid":17616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T17:22:48.000Z","msg":"我會唔去長崎，太晒時間，寧願多一日係廣島同岡山，或者唔去廣島去長崎，熊本唔會去住，因為阿蘇同熊本城未整好。"},{"pid":"5dacd2463174191dcdfb7761802f977867c4bffc","tid":29114,"uid":10425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T00:11:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黎近我都係九州廣島<br />\n不過鹿兒島做起點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鹿兒島有咩玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}